commit message: Use a custom background_light because it changed to white on ICS forward

Attempt to avoid an NPE processing search results

From crash reports I've gotten, it appears that onFinishedFetch() is getting
called in cases where the activity is no longer attached to the fragment. In
which case, we probably don't need to do anything. So rather than die, let's try
ignoring the response.
